mods.abstract: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing the Johnny Paycheck Show featuring Jim Ed Brown, the Cates Sisters, and Crystal Gayle at Dubuque Senior High School on March 16. Poster features metal photoplates of Johnny Paycheck, Jim Ed Brown, the Cates Sisters, and Crystal Gayle. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/39725.
